to be with all of you today

00:04:42.490 --> 00:04:47.850
at this most
important place that

00:04:47.850 --> 00:04:52.760
affects the whole world in
every moment, the headquarters

00:04:52.760 --> 00:04:53.300
of Google.

00:04:59.040 --> 00:05:05.613
With power comes a tremendous
